{"type": "article", "id": 3902, "title": "Fineck智能颈环", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-27T07:57:54Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233109baSK2zIAH4CrZdMf.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t现代上班族每天久坐办公桌，很容易就让肩颈背部的肌肉僵硬，引起偏头痛、脊椎侧弯酸痛等恼人问题。不少人会选择肩颈推拿或做颈部运动操的方式舒缓疼痛，现在维锐科技打算用更智能的方式帮你搞定这件事。日前，他们推出了一款名为「Fineck」的智能颈环，专注于颈部护理，它能够追踪颈部细微的移动动作，识别各种身体姿势，然后向用户传达身体的健康状态。当判定到颈椎有错误姿态及劳损时，Fineck 会震动提醒。它还提供多种颈椎互动游戏，帮助改善颈椎健康。目前，Fineck 正在<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/184140387/fineck-the-worlds-first-wearable-device-for-your-n\" target=\"_blank\"> Kickstarter </a>上众筹，起售价 69 美元。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233107kQOgiU0CtZBp9zNe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233107HRXht1Iw4JzvABys.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.634375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233108F9Ccz0bOr2mVUNS7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5609375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052331083juzC50hT6oBG9EQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052331091QWPR4xg3EpVSyCb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}